text-indent:21.0pt;line-height:22.0pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly">
MingyuLi,AssociateProfessor,receivedhisB.Eng.andPh.DfromDepartmentofOpticalEngineering,ZhejiangUniversity,China,in2001and2006,respectively.From2006to2008,hewasapostdoctoralfellowattheCenterforIntegratedOptoelectronics,ZhejiangUniversity,workingonintegratedopticalwaveguidesensor.In2009,heworkedatRoyalInstituteofTechnology,Sweden,asapostdoctoralfellowonphotoniccrystal.HereturnedtoZhejiangUniversityin2010andbecameanAssociateProfessorintheDepartmentofOpticalEngineering.Hiscurrentresearchinterestsfocusonintegratedoptics,bio-opticalsensorandsolarcells.Hehaspublishedover30scientificpapers.&nbsp;
			
				
